OL,3,CPolice could be given new powers to
OL,4,Ccrackdown on drug-impaired driving
OL,6,FThe report notes that a Drugs Limit
OL,7,FWorking Group was formed to identify
OL,8,Fdrug limits, which reviewed practices
OL,9,Fin the UK.
OL,11,FThe proposals initially focus on
OL,12,Flimits for cannabis, with Mr Jehan
OL,13,Fproposing a 5g/L (micrograms per
OL,14,Flitre) cannabis limit for drivers.
OL,16,FIn the UK, the limit for cannabis is
OL,17,F2g/L (micrograms per litre), but
OL,18,Fthere is also robust guidance on
OL,19,Flimits for other drugs, including
OL,20,Fcocaine, ketamine and medicinal drugs.
