OL,3,CPolice could be given new powers to
OL,4,Ccrackdown on drug-impaired driving
OL,6,FMr Jehan notes there may be "powers to
OL,7,Fadd further specified drugs by Order
OL,8,Fin the future".
OL,10,FThe report clarifies that lower
OL,11,Fcannabis limits may be in place for
OL,12,Fregistered driving instructors, those
OL,13,Fwho exceed the prescribed alcohol
OL,14,Flimit, or in cases where the vehicle
OL,15,Fcan only be driven by someone with a
OL,16,Fpublic service vehicle or Group 2
OL,17,Flicence.
OL,19,FThe proposals are set to be debated in
OL,20,Fthe States Assembly in March.
