OL,3,CPolice could be given new powers to
OL,4,Ccrackdown on drug-impaired driving
OL,6,FGuernsey introduced specified legal
OL,7,Flimits for driving under the influence
OL,8,Fof controlled drugs under its motoring
OL,9,Flaws, which were updated in March last
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FThe Bailiwick also introduced an
OL,13,Foffence of driving whilst over the
OL,14,Fprescribed drug limit.
